# Code owners for chocolatey-sonos-controller.
#
# Paths below require review from @fsch before merging. This is the in-repo
# half of the rule; the enforcement half lives in branch protection on `main`
# (require review from Code Owners). Without that branch-protection setting,
# CODEOWNERS only requests review, it does not require it.

# Publish and CI workflows — any change here can affect how CHOCO_API_KEY is used.
/.github/workflows/   @fsch
/.github/CODEOWNERS   @fsch

# Package definition — nuspec, install script, and anything that decides what
# ends up in the published .nupkg.
/chocolatey/          @fsch

# Legal and security surfaces.
/LICENSE              @fsch
/SECURITY.md          @fsch
/README.md            @fsch
